===Adjective===
'''single'''
# not accompanied by anything else
#:''"You can't give me a '''single''' reason as to why I shouldn't shoot your fucking head off!" the criminal yelled to the store clerk.''
# not divided in parts
# designed for the use of only one
# not [[married]]
#:''Josh put down that he was a '''single''', looking male on the dating website.''
# {{botany}} having only one rank or row of petal

